{
  "stem": "1733.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And keep on cooking, and-- and-- and-- and-- and their mouth was watering and dropping.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just the immediate people between ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody was taking care of themselves and trying to keep-- trying to-- to follow the orders of the kapos or of the SS.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they-- when they woke you up in the morning, you were trying to get up in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- you shouldn't have to be beaten.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or if you lagging, you were beat-- being beaten with sticks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to standing outside, and we were just huddling and moving between ourselves to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't hear any news of the war at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know how the war was going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rumors were in camp that the war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were having hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But nothing-- nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We really didn't know what was going on outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the food distribution was only once a day, that they gave you in the morning, or in the evening, the soup, the thin soup, which is very, very watery, and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what you ate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what you kept the sustenance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If people-- people towards-- towards the-- when you were there already a couple of-- a few weeks, and you were weakened from the-- from the labor, and people got sick, they got diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They recognized that they have to help themselves, because if they-- if they report for sick leave, they take you into the-- to the-- to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they let you die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't even give you any food there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were taking the bread, and they had a stove in-- in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were burning it, making charcoal out of it and healed-- healed themselves that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
